[Poke:infiniteEnergy:Infinite Energy]

Player 1 has infinite energy.

POKE 36220 0 (#R36218): LD (#N39371),A > LD (#N00203),A (tries to write in the ROM zone = does nothing).

POKE 36516 0 (#R36514): LD (#N39371),A > LD (#N00203),A (tries to write in the ROM zone = does nothing).

POKE 39371 200 (#R39371): If the code was ever patched to NOP, this poke restores RET Z, so P1 never decrements its energy.

Those pokes avoid the self-modify patch that enables the P1 depletion.